{"tid":2494952,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「現貨」100蚊6個台灣鳳梨","createTime":"2021-04-19T01:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T02:13:57.000Z","uid":159271,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"72f1dcfc773d6bb6db0fdb7c8638636238857d90","tid":2494952,"uid":159271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:41:28.000Z","msg":"網上見到，有手足比人棄單。<br />\n<br />\n想食平靚正台灣鳳梨盲去抬一箱走！<br />\n<br />\n鴨島鄉民 Ap Lei Man<br />\n15 小時  &middot; <br />\n【22:51 UPDATE: 感謝黃圈的愛🥰<br />\n我地暫時要熄一熄先份form，比啲時間島民統計下仲有幾多箱🙏🏻我地會係到update 大家🙇🏻&zwj;♀️】￼<br />\n￼<br />\n【棄單鳳梨🍍求收養🥺】<br />\n話說本區黃店 〝heunggongjai香港仔〞 早幾日同島民講<br />\n有香港人早排同個台灣果農訂左800箱鳳梨🍍<br />\n原本係想支持台灣果農🙌🏻<br />\n點知熱潮過左就比人棄單😭😭😭<br />\n希望可以成本價$100原箱6個散貨<br />\n除翻開都係17蚊個，真係又平又靚🥺<br />\nD貨星期一就到啦，希望大家多多益善，盡量幫手散貨🙏🙏🙏<br />\n自己食、送人都好啊🥺😂<br />\n但為行政方便，暫時只接受原箱購買<br />\n4月20號下星期二起，係位置黃竹坑既heunggongjai香港仔自取<br />\n有意想大批要嘅黃店歡迎PM我哋<br />\n鴨島鄉民幫手出車費💪💪💪<br />\n記住保持熱度啊！！！！<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/Pgopagv69BFrGpQg6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FPgopagv69BFrGpQg6&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=6360ac7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/Pgopagv69BFrGpQg6</a>"},{"pid":"939385473b202381f8ffc6c2a9ff91d0df0049b6","tid":2494952,"uid":159271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"369a28886f9186ebd47b3ca9004d1db56135ea8c","tid":2494952,"uid":198181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru